      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents a rare find for any discerning buyer. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory luster without a single chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is in pristine, like-new condition, with the leather upholstery still smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history; it drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions perfectly, making this a truly turn-key vehicle for its next owner.",
