      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, preserved in showroom condition. Every aspect of this automobile, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the secondary market. Mechanically sound and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this vehicle represents a premier acquisition for the discerning driver who demands excellence without compromise.",
