      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this\u2014it's in absolute pristine condition and basically looks and smells brand new! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a quick, smooth sale to a good home. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
