    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2011 BMW M3 (E92), a definitive example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 era. This specimen features a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory variable M-differential lock, providing unparalleled driver engagement. The naturally aspirated powerplant screams to an 8,400 RPM redline, with mechanical integrity bolstered by documented preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator services. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and precise suspension geometry. Presented in collector-grade condition, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory-fresh tactile feel. A mechanically flawless, turn-key investment for the purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
